::: {.callout-important}
**Action:** Prioritise steering for glass and body damage claims — the evidence shows a
clear, consistent cost benefit. Do not invest in expanding steering for total loss cases;
the savings are negligible and resources are better spent on compliance and valuation quality.
:::

